    {
      "id": "de8d23fc-b41f-4653-9c4e-0efd23c3d147",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The work groups courses according to similarity in student behaviors or by degree and how different feature engineering strategies affect model performance. Authors find that, while portability is possible, it is only achievable under certain constraints.",
